snippet.title: Killer Klowns from Outer Space - Official Trailer | IGN Fan Fest 2024
snippet.description:
Killer Klowns from Outer Space: The Game is an asymmetrical multiplayer horror based on the iconic '80s film. In the battle between Killer Klowns and the citizens of Crescent Cove, team up and use your wits to harvest humans or save them from the alien invasion! Killer Klowns from Outerspace is coming to Xbox, PlayStation, and PC.

#IGNFanFest
